      "content": "i know people say there's always hope but it just feels like a lie they tell to make themselves feel better. i've tried everything and i'm just... exhausted. like i'm actually past the point of being able to recover. it's not even about being sad anymore, it's just a fact that i'm fundamentally damaged. you can't fix something that's just inherently broken.",
